data.description: Welcome to 555 Marquette Ave! This beautiful split-level single-family home is nestled in the heart of Calumet City, offering the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. With its multi-tiered design, and hardwood flooring, this home maximizes space and offers separate areas for living, sleeping, and recreation. This 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath home has adequate living space that provides comfort and style. The main level boasts a spacious living room filled with natural light, perfect for entertaining guests or cozy evenings. Eat-in kitchen equipped with built-in appliances, ample cabinet space, and a dining area that overlooks the living room, making meal times a communal experience. The upper level features generously sized bedrooms with plenty of closet space and a contemporary bathroom. Lower level offers additional space, ideal for a family room, home office, or gym. A dedicated laundry area ensures convenience. Enjoy the outdoors in the well-maintained backyard, perfect for summer BBQs, gardening, or a peaceful morning coffee. Located on a beautiful block of Calumet City, you're close to local amenities, parks, schools, expressway and transportation. Additional amenities include an attached garage, side drive, central air conditioning. Roof less than 8yrs old. With its impeccable design and a prime location, 555 Marquette Ave is the perfect place to call home. Property sold AS-IS. With minor updates and improvements needed, this home is a WIN!
